# 0.0.6 - 14/02/2025
- Update `settings_sidebar.tsx` to render component tabs, in a single file, instead of separate component files grouped.
- Add separate folders for tabs component.
- Add `LanguageContext` as a better way to propagate languages, than prop drilling. May add libs later for this, but thats not the focus rn.
- Add Integrations image. Source: https://www.svgrepo.com/svg/436798/link-circle-fill [64px]
- Add Configuration gear image.* Source: https://icon-sets.iconify.design/mdi/gear/ [48px]
- Add Source Code github image. Source: https://icon-sets.iconify.design/octicon/mark-github-24/ [48px]
- Add Contributors group image. Source: https://icon-sets.iconify.design/flowbite/users-group-solid/ [48px]
- Add `Active` selection forthe menu & selection line to replicacte GOGs' configs menu.
- Add minimum window size in `tauri.conf.json`. [Next goal, is to make it frameless and add a personalized `title bar`]
- Priority for next version, is to implement the installation proccess & necessary repos to Orion repo. Also, to clean the css stylesheet.


